<topic id="dcpp_how_to_change_link_styles">
    <title>How to Change Link Styles</title>
    <body>
        <p>Let say you want the links to be bolded and with an underline. In your <xref
                href="dcpp_the_customization_css.dita">customization css</xref> add this snippet:</p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-css">*[class ~= "topic/xref"][href]:after,
*[class ~= "topic/link"][href]:after {
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: underline;
}</codeblock>
    </body>
</topic>
